The '''Second Warmaster''' was originally a [[Warrior caste|warrior]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. The warrior challenged the [[vua'sa]] that [[Yun-Yuuzhan]] had created and placed as [[warmaster]]. The vua'sa was defeated and [[Death/Legends|killed]], and the warrior took its place.

